'''Botirali Ergashev''' ([[Cyrillic|Uzbek Cyrillic]]: ''Ботирали Эргашев''; born 23 June 1995) is an [[Uzbekistan]]i [[association football|footballer]] who plays for [[FC Neftchi Fergana|Neftchi Fergana]] and [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]].

==International career==
Ergashev made his debut for the [[Uzbekistan national football team]] in a 1–0 friendly loss to [[Iran national football team|Iran]] on 19 May 2019.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://us.soccerway.com/matches/2018/05/19/world/friendlies/iran/uzbekistan/2702101/|title=Iran vs. Uzbekistan – 19 May 2018 – Soccerway|website=us.soccerway.com}}</ref>

